Check names for the code < block < chapter

Source: R/utils.R
check_names.Rd

Renames all of the entries in all_info vector as code, block or chapter

Usage

check_names(all_info)

Arguments

all_info

A vector with code < block < chapter or block < chapter or just chapter

Value

A vector with homogenous names
